== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|01-L 2009 track.png}}
5月中旬，有[[锋_(气象)|锋面系统]]在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]附近停止移动并缓慢瓦解。受[[低压槽|短波槽]]影响，该天气系统北部于5月25日向巴哈马以北移动。次日，位于[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]西南偏南方向约465公里的锋面系统边缘发展出[[低气压|低气压区]]。<ref name="TCR">{{cite web | author = Robbie Berg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023041925/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL012009_One.pdf | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-06-12 | accessdate = 2012-10-23 | title = Tropical Depression One Tropical Cyclone Report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL012009_One.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>系统向北移动，组织结构逐渐改善。5月27日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始针对位于北卡罗莱纳州[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）以南约195公里海域的低气压区发布热带天气展望。<ref name="TWO1">{{cite report | author1 = Landsea | author2 = Franklin | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-27 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook for the North Atlantic Ocean: May 27, 2009 8:05AM EST}}</ref>受东南方向的[[高气压|上层高压脊]]影响，系统转向东北<ref name="TWD2">{{cite report | author = Formosa | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-28 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion for the North Atlantic Ocean: May 28, 2009 2:05AM EST}}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月28日凌晨0点左右，美国国家飓风中心针对位于哈特拉期角以东约150公里洋面的低气压区发布最后一份展望，其中认为低气压不会得到进一步发展<ref name="TWO3">{{cite report | author1 = Berg | author2 = Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-27 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook for the North Atlantic Ocean: May 27, 2009 7:45PM EST}}</ref>。

5月28日，系统中的对流迅速再生，美国国家飓风中心因此再度开始发布热带天气展望。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当天下午15点左右，该机构将位于[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]][[普罗维登斯_(罗德岛州)|普罗维登斯]]以南约500公里海域的系统归类为第一号热带低气压。<ref name="ADV1">{{cite web | author1 = Franklin | author2 = Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Public Advisory One | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023031548/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2012-10-23 }}</ref>成为[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]后，低气压呈现出深层对流活动，其[[风眼|环流中心]]坐落在西北边缘。系统的重新发展是因多种利好因素的共同影响，如[[风切变|风切变]]少和高达26[[摄氏度|°C]]的[[海面温度|水温]]等。<ref name="D1">{{cite web | author1 = Franklin | author2 = Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023112614/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.001.shtml | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion One | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>当晚，低气压行经海域水温渐低，风切变也越来越多，气旋中的对流开始消亡。系统这时正夹在东南方向的[[高压脊|副热带高压脊]]和西北方向的[[低压槽|低压槽]]之间，与[[西风带|西风带]]连接起来<ref name="D2">{{cite web | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Two | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.002.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023031954/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.002.shtml | archivedate = 2012-10-23 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}深夜23点30分左右，一颗[[快速散射仪|快速散射仪]]卫星从低气压上空经过并测得热带风暴强度大风，但气象机构认为这一风速受到降雨的影响，所以不能代表低气压的实际强度。卫星过去后，气旋的环流中心开始朝西北方向部分暴露出来，关联的部分对流区也已消亡。<ref name="D3">{{cite web | author = Robbie Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Three | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.003.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023114959/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-23 }}</ref>
[[File:Precursor_to_TD_1_2009.jpg|thumb]]

5月29日清晨，第一号热带低气压一度接近热带风暴强度，通过[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]估算所得数值为{{lang|en|T}}2.5，相当于每小时65公里风速，但同样的分析得到的最低数据又只有{{lang|en|T}}1.5，代表的风力时速为55公里，仍属热带低气压标准{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带低气压是指[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]在每小时62公里以下的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}。对流活动在夜间经过爆发，到{{lang|en|UTC}}早上7点时，降水和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动又已消退。气旋这时已行进至墨西哥湾暖流边缘，因此气象部门预计低气压不大可能增强成热带风暴。{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带风暴是指持续风速在每小时63至118公里之间的热带气旋<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="D4">{{cite web | author1 = Brennan | author2 = Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Four | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023110937/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.004.shtml? }}</ref>当天上午，强烈的风切变令环流中心完全暴露，并且这时还有逐渐逼近的低压槽开始吸收规模较小的低气压。系统中的残余对流则局限在东南一角<ref name="D5">{{cite web | author1 = Kimberlain | author2 = Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Five | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023104808/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.005.shtml? }}</ref>。由于低气压周围已经没有对流继续发展，系统于5月29日下午退化成残留低气压区。{{lang|en|UTC}}当晚21点，美国国家飓风中心发布针对第一号热带低气压的最后一份公告<ref name="D6">{{cite web | author1 = Kimberlain | author2 = Franklin | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion Six (Final) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023115059/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al01/al012009.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。系统残留一直持续到{{lang|en|UTC}}5月30日早上6点，最终被[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]以南的一股[[暖锋|暖锋]]吸收<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施、影响和纪录 ==
5月27日，第一号热带低气压的前身天气系统在北卡罗莱纳州部分地区产生小雨<ref name="TWD2" />。哈特拉斯当天的降雨量为2.5毫米，持续风速为每小时24公里，阵风时速则有37公里。气象部门测得的最低[[气压|海平面气压]]为1009[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.81[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）。<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2008-05-27 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = History for Hatteras, NC: May 27, 2009 Weather | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620031948/http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/KHSE/2009/5/27/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA | archivedate = 2015-06-20 | url = http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/KHSE/2009/5/27/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA }}</ref>

北卡罗莱纳州海岸沿线的风速较高，这种情况有可能和低气压的外围边缘有关<ref>{{cite web | author = Rob Nucatola | publisher = WCTV | date = 2009-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | title = Tropical Depression One Forms | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150831155436/http://www.wctv.tv/home/headlines/46365517.html | archivedate = 2015-08-31 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wctv.tv/home/headlines/46365517.html }}</ref>。根据美国国家飓风中心的热带气旋报告，第一号热带低气压的形成位置比有纪录以来其它5月形成的热带气旋都更偏北面<ref name="TCR" />。

